          <source>In this task, you will create an empty <ph id="ph1">[!INCLUDE[avalon1](../../../includes/avalon1-md.md)]</ph> application by using the WPF Application Visual Studio template and add references to the appropriate <ph id="ph2">[!INCLUDE[netfx_current_short](../../../includes/netfx-current-short-md.md)]</ph> workflow assemblies.</source>
