          <source>In the <bpt id="p1">**</bpt>New Project<ept id="p1">**</ept> dialog box, select either <bpt id="p2">**</bpt>Visual C#<ept id="p2">**</ept> or <bpt id="p3">**</bpt>Visual Basic<ept id="p3">**</ept> from the <bpt id="p4">**</bpt>Installed Templates<ept id="p4">**</ept> pane on the left side of the box.</source>
